snippet.title: Elephant Rave 2 Game Announcement 🐘
snippet.description:
Elephant Rave 2 is a very free video game launching on Thursday, September 7 2023 for Steam, Itch, Armor Games, and Newgrounds. Come experience the joy of elephants by protecting this little one (again!) from extremely deadly lasers

Newgrounds + Armor: In-browser at launch!
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/950230/Elephant_Rave_2/
Itch: https://jmtb02.itch.io/elephant-rave-2
